textBlock: PRESIDENT TRUMP (CONT'D): But like President Ronald Rogaine, I will bring back the milk! They still want that milk. PRESIDENT TRUMP (CONT'D): A wall of milk. No criminals get through. Democrats want criminals to have the milk. No way. Milk comes from coal. We'll dig it up. All of the words are mispronounced. The crowd cheers. They hate pronounciations. They love milk. They start digging.
